				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yes, you will run out of lines eventually, but rather than shift all data manually you can adjust to the fact that the nametable will wrap around from line 29 to line 0 again, and write your lines there. Essentially, you'll need to treat the second nametable as a kind of circular buffer for pattern lines.
<br />
<br />Of course, this makes updating a little more akward and means you cannot keep your entire PPU version in the pattern all at once, only a portion of it, but it'll still save you PPU updates with the tradeoff of more complicated code for the nametable updates.</div>

